#Method void reset(const SkImageInfo& info) 

Sets width, height, SkAlphaType, and SkColorType from info.
Sets pixel address to nullptr. 
Sets row bytes to zero.

#Deprecated
Makes no sense to reset row bytes if width is not zero.
##

#Param info  ImageInfo ##

#NoExample
##

